In a large microwave safe bowl, heat margarine and marshmallows at HIGH for 3 minutes, stirring after 2 minutes. Mix peanut butter and vanilla into marshmallow mixture. Sir in vanilla and KELLOGG'S* RICE KRISPIES* cereal until well coated. Shape mixture into 13 (10 cm) balls. Use prepared chocolate frosting to pipe on markings and stitching. Best if served the same day.